items.name: Mogami (Kancolle)
items.description:
An experimental character LoRA of Mogami from Kantai Collection.

Info

Training with 66 images
Followed the manual form [ [Guide] Make your own Loras, easy and free ],
You can access to this guide in Suggested Resources section.

Recommended set up

Sampler: Euler a, DPM family series
Sampling steps: 20 or 25+
CFG Scale: 7
CLIP Skip: 2
*Do not use [restore face] on anime character!*

LoRA Weighting: [1 - 0.8], (1 - 0.65)

Baking Step:
0. Drafting (512 x 512 res to find your desired sketch)
1. Hires fix (txt2img: 768 x 768, 768 x 512, 512 x 768, or above res)
2. inpaint (img2img: refine some unwanted effect, [Euler a] with 50+ step)
3. Upscaling (img2img: res*2 with [ControlNet Tile] & Ultimate SD upscale)

Upscaler for [Step 1 - 3]: [R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, 4x-AnimeSharp, 4x-UltraSharp]
I always skip Step 0, 2 :P

Basic prompts

MogamiKC, serafuku, (brown) sailor collar, (black) neckerchief, (brown) shorts, (black) socks, boots
MogamiKaiNiKC, (KN) serafuku, (brown) shirt, (brown) sailor collar, (orange) neckerchief, (brown) shorts, (brown) socks

Some additional tags that you may use for reference

-swept bangs
-(long sleeves) serafuku, belt, kneehighs

[Kai Ni]
-(KN) sailor collar, (orange) sailor collar, (brown) neckerchief
-(light brown) sailor collar, (light brown) sleeve cuff

-green eyes
